Package customer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CustomerDAO
    Interface to implement DB read and write operations This interface will be implemented by any class responsible for reading and writing to specific data source
    DbReadOperations
    Interface to enforce all read operation from database
    DbWriteOperations
    Interface to enforce all read operation from database
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BankConstants
    Bank Constants to update promotions and fees
    CustomerData
    Class to create customer data and reading and writing customer object to database
    CustomerManager
    This class is responsible for implementing functionality to mange customer data It has a composition association with DnDriver and uses that for connecting to DB
    DbCreator
    This class is for one time database and table creation to store customer and account information
    DbDriver
    This class is responsible for setting connections and implementing all read and write operations to data base
